review.reviewBody: Great packaging and most importantly great taste!

Never get hashbrowns and if you order a side of $7 French toast it's only one piece of dempsters white bread. Eggs were ok. Sausages were gritty and fell apart 
Would give half star if I could
2 Roast lamb orders 10/10 this afternoon with my dad  great food!!!
Roast lamb dinner two orders ,This afternoon with my dad 10/10  !!!!

This is a dinosaur as these diners are part of history.  There food is the epitome of home cooking. I have eaten in their  restaurant as well as through Door dash . Their liver and onions is to die for and almost impossible to find at any restaurant any more . Today I had the cMontreal Smoked Meat Hash with eggs and hash browns. . I would highly recommend if you want home style food nothing fancy but big portions .
